description:
She steps down the theatre stage and starts her walk out of the cave, which is now drowned in light. Ancient mysteries lie deep under the multitude of stalactite and stalagmite clusters. As she walks away —  the stage becomes one with the texture of the cave, the memory of this place and of her dance dissolves with every step, leaving only a subtle echo, moving deep inside the grotto. 

Soundscape created by PAN BONKA

{2020 — chapter 3 of 3}
